MAGPIE

REFER A FRIEND TEMPLATE

The Magpie Template is an excellent option for your refer-a-friend program. This refer a friend template empowers your loyal customers with all the advocacy tools they need to successfully share your products, monitor referral activity, and get paid. It is perfect for your B2C referral programs, allows multiple payment options (PayPal, gift cards, and vouchers), and it's available in 20 languages.
This refer a friend template is built with Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is easily customizable, fully responsive, and supports all current browsers and devices.
TRY IT FREE
LIVE PREVIEW
This refer a friend template has no traditional registration and login forms. Access is provided via a seamless form where your existing customers enter their email addresses. You can also skip this step by using a one-click access link or adding your custom fields to this access form to collect additional information from your advocates.

The advocate stats section delivers deep insight into the referral program account, allowing the advocate to review their performance and focus on the advocacy tools that work. The advocate can quickly check the total referrals and rewards, the list of referrals, bonuses, and their status.

ADVOCATE INSIGHTS

ADVOCATE PAYMENT METHODS

There are multiple advocate payment methods available on this refer a friend template. When you activate several payment methods, your advocates can choose how they want to get paid. PayPal, Visa prepaid gift cards, and coupons are the best options for building a refer-a-friend program.
